Making Christ Known
We aim to help you share God’s Word with the lost every day. We price our material at or sometimes 
  below our cost on our larger quantities with the desire to help you reach as many souls as possible. You will 
  find a range of affordable options from the value-priced Standard Tracts through the Audio Tracts made 
  very affordable for giving with tips or to neighbors and friends.
Not every soul is at the same point in its awareness of its need. Some need to wake up to being sinners 
  before it’s too late; others are hungry for the truth and don’t know where to find it. In the past 
  few years, we’ve added a large number of new gospel tracts, tract cards and gospel calendar options 
  as well as new categories of gospel booklets and audio tracts. Some of these address modern ways of stating 
  old error, such as post-modernism. Others provide new children’s tracts for use in your Sunday School or 
  Vacation Bible School. With the Lord’s help, we will continue to offer newly-crafted messages with the 
  unfading story of God’s grace and man’s need. Keep checking for new options and titles.
We’d love your feedback. If you have any suggestions for ways we can serve you better, we’d 
  like to hear about it. Feel free to send your ideas for new tract messages as well. Please write to 
  BTPorders@bibletruthpublishers.com with your helpful thoughts.





 
        
   

      


      
   

    


 


